	<h2>Some Babies Grow Up Cowboys</h2>
	<p>Erickson's articles and essays have been published in Texas Highways, Oklahoma Today, Livestock Weekly, The Dallas Morning News, The Dallas Times Herald, and American Cowboy. Many of the pieces are anecdotal, based on Erickson's experiences and observations on ranches. Others requied some research and are more historical. Some are essays in which Erickson views contemporary life through the lens of cowboying.
		</p>
</div>

